description: Red Wraps is reeling in hungry Austinites by the hundreds with their healthy, delicious, and worldly offerings. Fusing the tastiest flavors from Southeast Asian & Middle Eastern cuisines, this trailer is serving up wraps that are really quite amazing. The signature Red Wrap is a charred tortilla containing 24 spice bulgur that has been friction cooked to perfection along with tomatoes & mild peppers, and drizzled with pomegranate sauce, lemon juice, and topped with lettuce. From there, you just add your favorite fixins' like chicken, hummus, avocado, etc...For this and many more wonderful wrapped creations, come head your way to this trailer and be ready to wrangle your appetite!
name: Red Wraps
